| Delta carrier frequencies | Will induce drowsiness / sleep. Wrong state for Drift. |
| High-energy rhythmic content | Activates sympathetic nervous system. Wrong direction. |
| Sudden silence or drops | Startle response. Breaks the ambient bubble. |
| Lyrics or intelligible speech | Engages language processing. Increases cognitive load. |

